# React

## Components

- **Functional components** — use hooks, no class components
- **Shared UI** — import from `../fijian` for screens; use `FijianCard`, `FijianInput`, etc.
- **Data** — `useApp()` for auth/game state; `data.js` for cast, events, bingo items
- **Small & focused** — one responsibility per component; extract reusable pieces

## Styling

- **Tailwind only** — no inline styles except dynamic values (e.g. `style={{ color: COLORS.player1 }}`)
- **Theme tokens** — `text-ochre`, `bg-fire-400`, `shadow-fire`, `animate-flicker`; never hex/rgba in JSX
- **Colors in JS** — import `COLORS` from `src/theme.js` for inline styles

## Accessibility

- `aria-label` on icon-only buttons
- `aria-pressed` for toggles
- `role="alert"` for errors
- Semantic HTML: `<header>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<article>`, `<nav>`
